{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act21side", "eventName": "敘拉古人", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "IS-ST-4", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "縫合", "storyInfo": "文明與蠻荒之間的衝突從未結束。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g2_srcalley", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rainlight_loop", "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shallowswalk", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_1502_crowns", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，尾巴弄濕了。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "char_1502_crowns"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還真是一點都沒變。無論是這些髒兮兮的街，還是煩死人的雨。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "char_1502_crowns"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道為什麼，烏薩斯的雪能要人命，可還是這裡的雨更讓人不爽。", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "char_1502_crowns"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但願老師家有吹風機......", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "char_1502_crowns"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師家就在這條巷子的盡頭。當年，弑君者懷著一腔怒火離開了這裡，為了證明自己已經足夠強大，能夠向籠罩她的那片陰雲復仇。"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今，柳德米拉又回來了。她的努力是否有給陰沉的天空打開一絲缺口，她自己都拿不準。"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許，其實什麼都沒改變，或許，她只是成了更大災難的幫兇。"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還好，柳德米拉還能回到這裡，她想，老師一定能告訴她接下來應該怎麼辦。"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "突然，她感到一陣惡寒。"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柳德米拉原本只是以為，這來源於自己即將再度面對老師的緊張。"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但馬上，她意識到自己錯了。"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她正在控制不住地戰慄。"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 3.0, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shallowsrun"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g8_srcroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$kjerag_n_intro", "key": "$kjerag_n_loop", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_1502_crowns"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師！！", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "char_1502_crowns"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "33_i16", "xScale": 1.6, "yScale": 1.6, "y": 300.0, "x": 350.0, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"duration": 10.0, "xTo": 250.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "33_i16", "xScale": 1.7, "yScale": 1.7, "y": 300.0, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"duration": 10.0, "xTo": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "33_i16", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "y": 150.0, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleTo": 0.88, "yScaleTo": 0.88, "duration": 30.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "化不開的血腥味。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的老師仰面倒在地上，鮮血仍在向外流淌蔓延。"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一把小刀掉落一邊。"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柳德米拉想要靠近，壓住老師仍在流血的傷口，但她發現自己無法挪動一步，她連視線都無法移開。"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一股讓她熟悉，又讓她恐懼的氣息正從陰影中浮現。"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "穿著紅色連帽衫，有著灰色頭髮的狼。"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真狼死了，紅聽了外婆的話。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是你。", "name": "柳德米拉"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g8_srcroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_1502_crowns", "name2": "char_144_red_7#1", "blackstart": 0.15, "blackend": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_1502_crowns", "name2": "char_144_red_7#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......做了什麼......", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "char_1502_crowns"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_1502_crowns", "name2": "char_144_red_7#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紅是獵狼人，紅聽外婆的話。", "name": "紅"}, "figure_art": "char_144_red_7#1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真狼死了，真狼沒有反抗。", "name": "紅"}, "figure_art": "char_144_red_7#1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_1502_crowns", "name2": "char_144_red_7#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你！！", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "char_1502_crowns"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "false", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 300.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_slash_02_s", "rox": 30.0, "x": 100.0, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$knifegore"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_ftrub"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_1502_crowns", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 0.2}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 40.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "false", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我殺了你！", "name": "柳德米拉"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_144_red_7#1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......紅答應過凱爾希，只殺狼，你不是狼。", "name": "紅"}, "figure_art": "char_144_red_7#1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_144_red_7#3"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來如此，她是你的凱爾希嗎？怪不得你身上有狼的氣味。", "name": "紅"}, "figure_art": "char_144_red_7#3"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_1502_crowns", "blackstart": 0.15, "blackend": 0.4}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......呼......老師明明已經沒辦法再戰鬥了，你為什麼還？！", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "char_1502_crowns"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_144_red_7#1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為外婆告訴紅，這就是遊戲規則。", "name": "紅"}, "figure_art": "char_144_red_7#1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，她出局啦。", "name": "紅"}, "figure_art": "char_144_red_7#1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紅要走了，紅還要找別的狼，他們就在附近。", "name": "紅"}, "figure_art": "char_144_red_7#1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_144_red_7#2"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（嗅嗅）", "name": "紅"}, "figure_art": "char_144_red_7#2"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_144_red_7#7"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，好像還有一隻狼也出局了，是有人比紅的動作更快嗎？", "name": "紅"}, "figure_art": "char_144_red_7#7"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_1502_crowns", "blackstart": 0.15, "blackend": 0.4}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "站住！", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "char_1502_crowns"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "穿著紅色連帽衫的狼沒有回應柳德米拉的呼喊，她哼著破碎的小調，邁著輕快的步伐從柳德米拉身邊掠過。"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柳德米拉伸出的手停在了半空。"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她突然想起，老師曾對她說："}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“柳德米拉，你知道成為我的學生意味著什麼嗎？”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我已經殘廢了，沒什麼大用，你卻甘願成為我的學生，我的工具？”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "“我們都會後悔的，孩子。”", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_1502_crowns", "fadetime": 0.5, "blackstart": 0.15, "blackend": 0.4}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "柳德米拉跪倒在地。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“吞下死難者的苦”......", "name": "柳德米拉"}, "figure_art": "char_1502_crowns"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g4_srctheater", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spotlightc"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_applause"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不愧是卡特琳娜女士醞釀了如此之久的作品。", "name": "激動的觀眾"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "切利尼娜在劇中，作為一個完美的敘拉古人形象，到最後竟才被揭示出是一個所有敘拉古人構建出的幻象。", "name": "激動的觀眾"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，正因為她在市井傳聞中是眾所周知的完美形象，用一種共同的想像去解釋她竟也是合理的。", "name": "激動的觀眾"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後點出她並不存在的那一幕，實在是太讓我震撼了。", "name": "激動的觀眾"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是意味深長的結尾。", "name": "激動的觀眾"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前陣子的廣播事件，還有後面那半天的混亂，我差點以為沃爾西尼就要這麼完了。", "name": "激動的觀眾"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結果現在還能看到這麼優秀的作品，唉，活著還是有價值的啊。", "name": "激動的觀眾"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可不是嗎。", "name": "興奮的觀眾"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，我當時以為天都要塌下來了。", "name": "興奮的觀眾"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒想到最後會是那樣的結果。", "name": "興奮的觀眾"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，你打不打算搬去新城市？", "name": "興奮的觀眾"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看情況吧，不過，如果新城市也有卡特琳娜女士的作品，我應該會去吧。", "name": "激動的觀眾"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟......家族不會入駐的城市，我長這麼大都沒敢想過。", "name": "激動的觀眾"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼說起來......你知道嗎？", "name": "興奮的觀眾"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡特琳娜女士好像在籌備一部新的作品。", "name": "興奮的觀眾"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新的作品？", "name": "激動的觀眾"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，這部作品光是標題，就已經足夠吸引人了。", "name": "興奮的觀眾"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "叫做——《敘拉古人》。", "name": "興奮的觀眾"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rainheavy_loop", "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g5_srcpark", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shovel", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一鏟，又一鏟。"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "墓園之中，萊昂圖索正在奮力地挖掘著墓穴。"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他的身邊是一口棺木，裡面躺著他的父親——貝納爾多。"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天是曾經的貝洛內家族領袖，貝納爾多的葬禮。"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "身為十二家族之一的領袖，參加其葬禮的人原本應當擠滿整個墓園。"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而，沒有人會參加一個背叛了家族，背叛了城市，背叛了時代之人的葬禮。"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊昂圖索也謝絕了拉維妮婭等人的參加。"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是他與父親最後的告別。"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "父親，你說，後人會怎麼評價你呢。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是開創了新時代的人，還是背叛了舊時代的人？", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許，這要看我接下來的成果而定吧，哈哈。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#3$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真是給我出了個大難題啊。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#2$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，該說我不愧是你的兒子嗎，也是真虧我接住了。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#8$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shovel", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊昂圖索一邊挖著，一邊像是父親還活著一樣，輕快地說著。"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除此之外，他不知道還能說些什麼。"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，西西里夫人同意了我的請求。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新的移動城市，將不會有家族入駐。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的夢想也算是實現了一部分吧。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在和西西里夫人交流過後，我終於理解了一點。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一位絲毫不介意在死後將敘拉古帶入墓穴。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她對於敘拉古只能在她活著時維持和平毫無負擔，敘拉古不需要未來。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該怎麼說呢......西西里夫人，比起一個統治者，她似乎更像是一個舊時代的看守者。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她願意給我機會，也只是因為，我給出的答案，讓她認為或許可以嘗試一下，僅此而已。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是一位可怕的存在。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哦，原本以為要挖個半天，沒想到，比我想得要輕鬆一些。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "墓穴的大小已經足夠，剩下的，就是將棺木埋入其中。"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊昂圖索走到棺木前，猶豫了一下，但終於還是伸出手。"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "棺木很沉，他推起來很費力。"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而就在他感到吃力時，他感覺到，身邊忽然出現了一個人在幫他推。"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他轉頭看去，那是德米特里。"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dragsofa", "loop": "true", "channel": "b"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "b", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 15.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown3"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "德米特里，你......", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "33_i07", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"duration": 60.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "德米特里沒有說話，他只是從自己外套的口袋裡，掏出一樣微微閃著銀光的東西，丟入墓穴中。"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是一塊懷錶。"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這是首領......這是他曾經送我的懷錶。", "x": 500.0, "y": 250.0, "alignment": "right", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "現在，也算是物歸原主了。", "x": 400.0, "y": 250.0, "alignment": "right", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "......", "x": 250.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你已經向我道過歉了，萊昂圖索。", "x": 500.0, "y": 250.0, "alignment": "right", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "只不過，即使我可以原諒你，在這次動亂裡死去的兄弟也不會原諒你。", "x": 700.0, "y": 250.0, "alignment": "right", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 400.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "即使貝洛內家族不復存在，我也不會忘記他們。", "x": 500.0, "y": 250.0, "alignment": "right", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我聽說了，你打算重組一個新的家族。", "x": 250.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "活下來的大部分人都離開了，但是，依然有留下來的人，他們需要一個安身之所。", "x": 700.0, "y": 250.0, "alignment": "right", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 450.0}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "即使那在你看來，是落後的家族。", "x": 450.0, "y": 250.0, "alignment": "right", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "......這樣也好。", "x": 250.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你走的是一條荊棘之路。", "x": 400.0, "y": 250.0, "alignment": "right", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我知道。", "x": 250.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "到時候，我依然會攔在你的路上。", "x": 450.0, "y": 250.0, "alignment": "right", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我知道。", "x": 250.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "別隨便死了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 250.0, "alignment": "right", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"duration": 5.0, "xTo": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shallowswalk"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "33_i07", "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1, "x": 150.0, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"duration": 30.0, "xTo": 200.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雨點的聲音嘈雜，但萊昂圖索依然聽到了最後這句話的末尾，有一聲輕輕的“萊昂”。"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也是，德米特。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他抬起頭，任由雨點打在臉上。"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g11_mansionhall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#6$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#6$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些傢俱，大部分都用不上了吧。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#6$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟，貝洛內家族已經不復存在了。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "絕大多數曾經的家族成員已經離開了這裡，他們......任何人都很難接受來自自己領袖的背叛。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "貝納爾多這個幾乎已經站在家族統治最高點的人，卻否定了家族的存在本身。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也否定了很多我們曾視若珍寶的東西。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "榮耀、信任、忠誠、為了家族的奉獻......", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "父親曾教導每一位家族成員遵守這些規矩，到頭來，他自己卻從未相信過這些嗎？", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我不知道。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#8$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這幾天，我時常在想。我有曾觸及過那個真正的貝納爾多·貝洛內嗎？", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#8$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白日劇團的藝術總監是他的偽裝，貝洛內家族老謀深算的領袖是他的偽裝......", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#8$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼有沒有可能，那個曾和我談起他的理想，帶著笑容，兩眼放光的貝納爾多也是他的偽裝呢？", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#8$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不重要了，已經不那麼重要了。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#2$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊昂，你和他，一起讓那座新的城市真正有了誕生的機會。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許吧。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "搬家的車很快就會來了。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我知道了。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一切並不是徒勞無功，萊昂。", "name": "拉維妮婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們會在新城區......不，現在是新城市了，建起些新的東西的。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_4065_judge_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "敘拉古未曾出現過的，嶄新的——", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "屬於每個人的秩序。", "name": "萊昂圖索"}, "figure_art": "avg_427_vigil_1#7$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊昂圖索看向拉維妮婭，他的眼中，閃爍著果決。"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "文明。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.5, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g26_dusk_wild", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自誕生那一刻起，每一頭狼都知道，自己的存在即是荒野的象徵。"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "經過漫長的時光，無數次的廝殺，他們最終選擇了以如今這種遊戲的方式選出頭狼。"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對扎羅來說，這一局的慘敗無疑是他的恥辱。"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他們生生不息。"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要等到下一輪遊戲開始，他馬上就能捲土重來。"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為此，他已經開始了物色人選。"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並且，他立刻發現了離開沃爾西尼，漫步於荒野的拉普蘭德。"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而——"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_683_1#6$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈......哈......", "name": "拉普蘭德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_683_1#6$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_683_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休息夠了嗎，扎羅。", "name": "拉普蘭德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_683_1#10$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_688_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_688_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "扎羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_688_1#1$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "扎羅與拉普蘭德在荒野上戰鬥了三個月。"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "期間，扎羅有無數次機會咬開這個狂人的脖子。"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她絕無可能真的戰勝他。"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，他卻逐漸明白，是他，絕無可能戰勝她。"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的血肉無法滋養任何思想，她的頭顱無法稱頌任何勝利，她的死亡毫無意義。"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是一具被填滿的空殼。"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她也是荒野？"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，她是荒蕪。"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他在一瞬間理解，如果貝納爾多的背叛是一種意料之外的情理之中，那麼眼前的存在，在他的理解之外。"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，他也曾見過這樣的人類，她絕非獨一無二。"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她卻是其中唯一一個在這獨一無二的時刻出現在他面前的人。"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一種預兆。"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一種呼喚。"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是，千百年來，荒野的化身，第一次，或許也將是最後一次向一個人類伏下身軀。"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他選擇向未知放下尊嚴。"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_683_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不打了？", "name": "拉普蘭德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_683_1#1$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_688_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的鬥爭將會持續千年萬年。", "name": "扎羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_688_1#1$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_688_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在分出勝負之前，我會與你同行。", "name": "扎羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_688_1#1$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_683_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，隨你的便。", "name": "拉普蘭德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_683_1#8$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉普蘭德無力地丟下武器，她的身體早已失去知覺。"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在她倒下之前，扎羅走過去，理所當然一般地，用自己的身軀托住了她。"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "德克薩斯，我們選擇了不同的道路毀滅敘拉古。", "name": "拉普蘭德"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很期待，我們下一次的見面。", "name": "拉普蘭德"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_dim_closeeye", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她閉上雙眼，沉沉睡去。"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒼茫的原野上別無他物，一時間，彷彿天地之間，只剩下一人，一狼。"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wolflordroar_1", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "蠻荒。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.5, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}